00:40:20,501 --> 00:40:22,837
- Were you in the hospital?
- I did.

524
00:40:28,759 --> 00:40:30,344
You discovered something important.

525
00:40:31,554 --> 00:40:33,472
So-hee's corpse is indeed there.

526
00:40:34,098 --> 00:40:37,852
You're going! I don't even know how much money I would ask for.

527
00:40:37,935 --> 00:40:39,270
Who did it?

528
00:40:40,062 --> 00:40:42,731
The amount depends on who killed her.

529
00:40:42,815 --> 00:40:45,401
- What if I tell you?
-Tell me, who?

530
00:40:46,485 --> 00:40:47,486
The rest is easy.

531
00:40:48,404 --> 00:40:50,322
I will torture that person day and night.

532
00:40:50,406 --> 00:40:52,241
He won't be able to eat or sleep.

533
00:40:52,324 --> 00:40:54,493
I'll beat her

534
00:40:56,120 --> 00:40:57,872
and hand it over to you.

535
00:41:00,541 --> 00:41:02,626
I know I'm not.

536
00:41:02,710 --> 00:41:04,420
Are any of them four?

537
00:41:05,713 --> 00:41:08,382
<i>Sa-ra? Did she kill her while she was high?</i>

538
00:41:10,134 --> 00:41:10,968
<i>Yeon-jin?</i>

539
00:41:12,052 --> 00:41:13,888
<i>She is the scariest of them all.</i>

540
00:41:14,638 --> 00:41:16,098
<i>Hye-jeong?</i>

541
00:41:16,182 --> 00:41:19,685
<i>She killed So-hee if she exposed her</i>
<i>and physical education teacher.</i>

542
00:41:20,561 --> 00:41:24,482
<i>Jae-jun? The bastard killed So-hee</i>
<i>if she mentioned his eyes.</i>

543
00:41:25,608 --> 00:41:27,610
Now we are in the same mess.

544
00:41:28,235 --> 00:41:31,572
Which one of them killed So-hee?

545
00:41:44,627 --> 00:41:47,421
Dong-eun asked you for money? How much?

546
00:41:47,505 --> 00:41:50,466
I don't know. She threw the bag
and told me to fill it.

547
00:41:50,549 --> 00:41:52,843
Fuck it! The bag is huge!

548
00:41:53,928 --> 00:41:56,347
- Why don't you answer me?
- When did you call me?

549
00:41:56,430 --> 00:41:57,932
- Not you.
- He's talking to you.

550
00:41:58,015 --> 00:42:00,434
She didn't visit you?

551
00:42:01,018 --> 00:42:02,603
He doesn't want money.

552
00:42:03,270 --> 00:42:05,314
I offered her money. She refused.

553
00:42:05,397 --> 00:42:08,651
Why can't I get Myeong-o?
You fired him?

554
00:42:08,734 --> 00:42:11,862
He won't know he's fired
because it doesn't answer me.

555
00:42:11,946 --> 00:42:12,780
Neither does she.

556
00:42:12,863 --> 00:42:16,659
Do you remember high school well?

557
00:42:16,742 --> 00:42:18,077
How is Ye-sol?

558
00:42:18,577 --> 00:42:19,662
Who is guarding her?

559
00:42:19,745 --> 00:42:21,830
What exactly did we do Dong-eun?

560
00:42:23,457 --> 00:42:24,291
Was it bad?

561
00:42:24,375 --> 00:42:26,168
She didn't throw her bag in front of you?

562
00:42:26,835 --> 00:42:29,421
Hell! She must have seen a lot of movies.

563
00:42:29,922 --> 00:42:31,590
Crazy woman wants dollars!

564
00:42:31,674 --> 00:42:33,676
Ye-sol is already in elementary school?

565
00:42:33,759 --> 00:42:35,594
Which one? The one in Semyeong?

566
00:42:35,678 --> 00:42:39,765
If he wants us to suffer,
what would you do to us?

567
00:42:39,848 --> 00:42:41,642
I didn't buy her a bag.

568
00:42:42,476 --> 00:42:43,561
What class is it?

569
00:43:03,205 --> 00:43:06,041
Tell me where you're going
and do you want a return ticket.

570
00:43:06,125 --> 00:43:09,378
I've always wanted to try this.

571
00:43:10,504 --> 00:43:13,090
I didn't think I would see it.

572
00:43:18,262 --> 00:43:20,347
To Vladivostok, in one direction.

573
00:43:21,140 --> 00:43:25,436
I think about you all day.

574
00:43:26,020 --> 00:43:27,146
Shall we meet?

575
00:43:28,272 --> 00:43:29,607
Fuck off.

576
00:43:29,690 --> 00:43:32,192
Do you want to see me alone? Why?

577
00:43:32,276 --> 00:43:35,154
Why do you want to meet me?

578
00:43:35,237 --> 00:43:37,323
Who? Son Myeong-o?

579
00:43:37,406 --> 00:43:39,491
You cunt, where are you?

580
00:43:39,575 --> 00:43:42,077
And Yeon-jin? Did you arrange a meeting with her?

581
00:44:03,474 --> 00:44:04,308
Me...

582
00:44:05,809 --> 00:44:06,644
<i>I...</i>

583
00:44:12,149 --> 00:44:13,067
Mori.

584
00:44:17,821 --> 00:44:18,864
<i>I'm dead.</i>

585
00:44:19,365 --> 00:44:26,330
IT'S BORING ME

586
00:46:22,029 --> 00:46:27,034
Subtitle translation: Davor Fröbe


